allows computers to extract patterns from
data and that could be structured data,

25
00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:13.970
in the form of numerical data, or
unstructured data, in the form of text,

26
00:02:13.970 --> 00:02:18.630
or other elements including pictures,

27
00:02:18.630 --> 00:02:22.700
