00:03:01.985 --> 00:03:06.610
NAIT, so the National Association
of Insurance Commissioners,

39
00:03:06.610 --> 00:03:10.950
indicates that only about 10 to
15 percent of the data collected

40
00:03:10.950 --> 00:03:14.600
