00:03:36.726 --> 00:03:41.510
Of course, the historical data in the form

47
00:03:41.510 --> 00:03:47.060
of the history of losses may not be
the only data that are important

48
00:03:47.060 --> 00:03:53.030
in understanding how to price risk and
how to predict the risk.

49
00:03:53.030 --> 00:03:57.460
Insurers could create models to predict
demand for their own products and

