decision making process,

65
00:05:18.930 --> 00:05:23.250
they can flag risks in the process,
and they can also point out

66
00:05:23.250 --> 00:05:27.870
inconsistencies in data that human
underwriters may not be able to see.

67
00:05:27.870 --> 00:05:32.599
They can also check external sources,
like social media,

68
00:05:32.599 --> 00:05:35.351
